BIG DEAD - Former Self

Title track off our most recent EP released June of 2022

Any money raised from this drop and our catalog pressing will go back into mixing and mastering our next aural offering. 

(We spent a week in Airlock Studios 2nd-9th of January 2023 and have something special on the way.)

Produced by Cam Bower and Big Dead
Mixed by Cody McWaters
Mastered by Rafael Anton Irrisari at Black Knoll Studio
credits
released June 22, 2022

Big Dead is:

Cam Bower - Guitar, Vocals
Josh Dunn - Guitar, Vocals
Lee Brackenborough - Keys, Synths
Lachlan Kidd - Bass Clarinet
Nathan MacGregor - Drums
